snippet.title: Jardin | A procedural walk on an endless lake
snippet.description:
Gardens say a lot about who you are.

Play the game for free : https://kaemelo.itch.io/jardin

Jardin is a poetic and procedural walk on an endless lake, with segmented parts of XIX's french poems. Wander and build your own garden, with your unique path.
